    "instructions": [
      "STEP 1 (2 min) — Unpack & sort: Separate fridge items from pantry items. Put dairy, produce, chickens, and milk straight in fridge. Leave oats, rice pouches, crackers, peanut butter, tuna/salmon cans, soy sauce on bench or pantry shelf.",
      "STEP 2 (2 min) — Portion oat bags: Measure 80g of oats into each of 7 zip-lock bags. Label Mon–Sun. Store in pantry. Each morning, tip one bag into a bowl, add 200ml milk, stir in psyllium husk, microwave.",
